
LordsAWar! version 0.3.2, a clone of the turn-based strategy game Warlords II, has been released with the following changes:

 * now using a new dark theme.
 * moved the scenario builder to the main menu.
 * added zoom in/out on the main map.
 * added 2-finger scrolling.
 * added a popup context menu for stacks.
 * now showing the army bonus in the city window.
 * added a new french translation.  Thanks James!

Please donate to the LordsAWar project so that we can get better artwork! Click on the donate button here: http://lordsawar.nongnu.org
